Description_lang: Your attacks slowly build Concussive Force, granting [low] attack power per stack. At X stacks, your next 3 melee abilities emit a shockwave in front of you, dealing bonus Nature damage to all enemies in a line. Shockwaves deal more damage to enemies at high health.
